quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  68,43,un ki ankhen jhuki hui hon gi aur un par zillat chhaa rahi hogi halaank pehlay ( uss waqt ) sjday ke liye bulatay jatay they jab ke sahih o salim they
  68,44,to mujh ko is kalaam ke jhutlanay walon se samajh lainay do. hum un ko aahista aahista aisay tareeq se pakren ge ke un ko khabar bhi nah hogi
  68,45,aur mein un ko mohlat diye jata hon meri tadbeer quwwat hai
  68,46,kiya tum un se kuch ajar mangte ho ke un par tawwan ka boojh par raha hai
  68,47,ya un ke paas ghaib ki khabar hai ke ( usay ) likhte jatay hain
  68,48,to apne perwar-digaar ke hukum ke intzaar mein sabr kiye raho aur machhli ( ka luqmah honay ) walay Younis ki terhan raho na ke unhon ne ( khuda ) ko puraka aur woh ( gham o ) ghusse mein bharay hue they
  68,49,agar tumahray perwar-digaar ki meharbani un ki yavri nah karti to woh chtil maidan mein daal diye jatay aur un ka haal ab-tar hojata
  68,50,phir perwar-digaar ne un ko bargzida karkay naiko karon mein karliya
  68,51,aur kafir jab ( yeh ) nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) suntay hain to yun lagtay hain ke tum ko apni nigahon se phsla den ge aur kehte yeh to deewana hai
  68,52,aur ( logo ) yeh ( quran ) ahal aalam ke liye nasiyaat hai
  69,1,sach much honay wali
  69,2,woh sach mach honay walikiya hai ?
  69,3,aur tum kokiya maloom hai ke sach mach honay walikiya hai ?
  69,4,khurkhranay wali ( jis ) ko smod aur Aad ( dono ) ne jhatlaya
  69,5,so smod to kadak se halaak kardiye gay
  69,6,rahay Aad to un ka nihayat taiz aandhi se satyanaas kardiya gaya
  69,7,khuda ne is ko saat raat aur aath din lagataar un par chalaye rakha to ( ae mukhatib ) to logon ko is mein ( is terhan ) dhaye(giray) ( aur marey ) parre dekhay jaisay khajoron ke khokhle tanay
  69,8,bhala to un mein se kisi ko bhi baqi daikhta hai ?
